\c 15
\s Ukungalaleli kukaSawuli, lokulahlwa kwakhe
\p
\v 1 USamuweli wasesithi kuSawuli: IN\nd kosi\nd* yangithuma ukuthi ngikugcobe ube yinkosi phezu kwabantu bayo, phezu kukaIsrayeli; ngakho-ke lalela ilizwi lamazwi eN\nd kosi\x + 9.16.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 2 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla \add ithi\add*: Ngizananzelela lokho uAmaleki akwenza kuIsrayeli\x + 27.8. 28.18. 30.1. Eks. 17.8,14,16. Nani 14.45. 24.20. Dute. 25.17-19. 2 Sam. 8.12. 1 Lan. 4.43. Hlab. 83.7. Hlu. 3.13.\x*, ukuthi wema njani emelene laye endleleni ekwenyukeni kwakhe eGibhithe\x + 1 Kho. 20.12.\x*.
\v 3 Hamba-ke uyetshaya uAmaleki, utshabalalise konke alakho; ungamyekeli\x + Levi 27.28,29. Josh. 6.17,21.\x*, kodwa ubulale kusukela kowesilisa kusiya kowesifazana, kusukela kusane kusiya komunyayo, kusukela enkabini kusiya emvini, kusukela ekamelweni kusiya kubabhemi\x + 22.19.\x*.
\p
\v 4 USawuli wasebiza abantu\x + 23.8.\x*, wababala eTelayimi, izinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili abahamba ngenyawo, lamadoda azinkulungwane ezilitshumi akoJuda\x + Josh. 15.24.\x*.
\v 5 USawuli wasefika emzini kaAmaleki, wacathama esigodini.
\v 6 USawuli wasesithi kumaKeni\x + 27.10. Hlu. 1.16.\x*: Hambani, lisuke, lehle liphume phakathi kwamaAmaleki, hlezi ngilibhubhise kanye lawo; ngoba lina lenza umusa kubo bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli ekwenyukeni kwabo bephuma eGibhithe\x + Eks. 18.10,19. Nani 10.29,32.\x*. Ngakho amaKeni asuka aphuma phakathi kwamaAmaleki.
\v 7 USawuli wasetshaya amaAmaleki\x + 14.48.\x*, kusukela eHavila\x + Gen. 2.11.\x* uze uyefika eShuri ephambi kweGibhithe\x + 27.8. Gen. 16.7.\x*.
\v 8 Wambamba uAgagi inkosi yamaAmaleki ephila; labo bonke abantu wabatshabalalisa ngobukhali benkemba\x + 27.8. 30.1.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa uSawuli labantu bamyekela uAgagi, lokuhle kakhulu kwezimvu lokwenkomo, lokunonisiweyo, lamawundlu, lakho konke okuhle; kabathandanga ukukutshabalalisa, kodwa yonke into edelelekayo lecakileyo bayitshabalalisa\x + 15.3,15. 28.18.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Kwasekufika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuSamuweli lisithi:
\v 11 Sengizisola ngokuthi ngambeka uSawuli waba yinkosi; ngoba ubuyele emuva ekungilandeleni, kaqinisanga amazwi ami. USamuweli wasethukuthela, wakhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ubusuku bonke.
\v 12 USamuweli wasevuka ekuseni kakhulu ukuhlangabeza uSawuli; kwasekutshelwa uSamuweli kuthiwa: USawuli usefikile eKharmeli; khangela-ke, uzimisele insika, wabhoda, wedlula, wehlela eGiligali.
\v 13 USamuweli wasefika kuSawuli; uSawuli wathi kuye: Kawubusiswe yiN\nd kosi\nd*; ngiliqinisile ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 14 USamuweli wasesithi: Kuyini pho lokhukukhala kwezimvu endlebeni zami, lokubhonsa kwenkomo engikuzwayo?
\v 15 USawuli wasesithi: Babuye lazo kumaAmaleki; ngoba abantu bayekele okuhle kakhulu kwezimvu lokwenkomo ukuze bahlabele iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho; kodwa okuseleyo sikutshabalalisile.
\v 16 USamuweli wasesithi kuSawuli: Yekela, ngikutshele ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* itheni kimi kulobubusuku. Wasesithi kuye: Khuluma.
\v 17 USamuweli wasesithi: Angithi, lapho usemncinyane emehlweni akho, waba yinhloko yezizwe zakoIsrayeli, leN\nd kosi\nd* yakugcoba waba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli?
\v 18 IN\nd kosi\nd* ikuthumile-ke ngendlela yathi: Hamba uyetshabalalisa izoni, amaAmaleki, ulwe lawo aze aphele\x + 9.21.\x*.
\v 19 Pho, kungani ungalilalelanga ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, kodwa waphaphela impango, wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 14.32.\x*\nd*?
\v 20 USawuli wasesithi kuSamuweli: Isibili ngililalele ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, ngihambile ngendlela iN\nd kosi\nd* ebingithume ngayo, ngibuyile loAgagi inkosi yakoAmaleki, njalo ngitshabalalisile amaAmaleki\x + 15.13.\x*.
\v 21 Kodwa abantu bathethe okwempango, izimvu lenkomo\x + 15.15.\x*, okuhle kwezinto ebezizatshabalaliswa, ukuze bahlabele iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eGiligali\x + Levi 27.28,29. Josh. 6.17,21.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa uSamuweli wathi: Kambe iN\nd kosi\nd* iyathokoza ngeminikelo yokutshiswa lemihlatshelo, njengekulaleleni ilizwi leN\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 40.6-8. 50.8,9. Zaga 21.3. Isa. 1.11-17. Jer. 7.22,23. Heb. 10.6-9.\x*\nd*? Khangela, ukulalela kungcono kulomhlatshelo, lokuqaphelisa kulamahwahwa ezinqama\x + Tshu. 5.1. Hos. 6.6. Mat. 9.13. 12.7. Mika 6.6-8. Mark. 12.33.\x*.
\v 23 Ngoba umvukela u\add njenge\add*sono sokuvumisa, lobuqholo buyisiphambeko lokukhonza izithombe\x + Gen. 31.19.\x*. Ngoba ulalile ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, layo ikwalile ukuthi ungabi yinkosi\x + 13.14.\x*.
\p
\v 24 USawuli wasesithi kuSamuweli: Ngonile; ngoba ngeqile umlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* lamazwi akho\x + 26.21.\x*; ngoba ngesaba abantu, ngakho ngalalela ilizwi labo\x + 12.14. Zaga 29.25.\x*.
\v 25 Ngakho-ke ake uthethelele isono sami, ubuyele lami, ukuze ngikhonze iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 26 Kodwa uSamuweli wathi kuSawuli: Kangiyikubuyela lawe ngoba ulalile ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, layo iN\nd kosi\nd* ikwalile ukuthi ungabi yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 15.23. 16.1.\x*.
\v 27 Kuthe uSamuweli etshibilika ukuthi ahambe, wabamba umphetho wesembatho sakhe, sasesidabuka\x + 1 Kho. 11.30,31.\x*.
\v 28 USamuweli wasesithi kuye: IN\nd kosi\nd* iwudabule kuwe lamuhla umbuso wakoIsrayeli, yawunika umakhelwane wakho ongcono kulawe\x + 28.17,18.\x*.
\v 29 Futhi-ke aMandla kaIsrayeli kawaqambi manga, kawazisoli, ngoba kawasimuntu ukuthi azisole\x + Nani 23.19.\x*.
\v 30 Wasesithi: Ngonile, ake ungihloniphe khathesi phambi kwabadala babantu bakithi laphambi kukaIsrayeli, ubuyele lami, ukuthi ngikhonze iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho.
\v 31 Ngakho uSamuweli wabuyela elandela uSawuli; uSawuli wayikhonza-ke iN\nd kosi\x + 15.25.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 32 USamuweli wasesithi: Msondezeni kimi uAgagi inkosi yakoAmaleki. UAgagi wasesiya kuye ethokozile; uAgagi wathi: Isibili ukubaba kokufa sekudlulile.
\v 33 USamuweli wasesithi: Njengoba inkemba yakho yemuke abesifazana abantwana, ngokunjalo unyoko uzakwemukwa abantwana phakathi kwabesifazana\x + Hlu. 1.7.\x*. USamuweli wasemhlahlela uAgagi phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Hlu. 8.21.\x*\nd* eGiligali\x + 15.12,21.\x*.
\p
\v 34 USamuweli wasesiya eRama\x + 1.19.\x*, loSawuli wenyukela endlini yakhe eGibeya kaSawuli\x + Josh. 18.28.\x*.
\v 35 USamuweli kaphindanga wambona uSawuli kwaze kwaba lusuku lokufa kwakhe\x + 19.24.\x*, kodwa uSamuweli wamlilela uSawuli\x + 16.1.\x*; leN\nd kosi\nd* yazisola ngokuthi yayimbekile uSawuli abe yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 15.11.\x*.